name: Vine Monogram Necklace
description:
Vine Monogram Necklace

This personalized, custom made acrylic necklace is laser cut from acrylic in the circle font, in the chain finish (gold/silver), acrylic color and monogram (three letters) of your choice.  Please allow 2-3 weeks for delivery

Item Details:
• Laser cut from 1/8 inch thick acrylic, measures 1.5 inches wide by 1.5 inches tall
• Includes an 18" silver or gold finished chain with a lobster clasp and one inch extender.
• Choose color from the color options photo.

Please specify the three letters in the EXACT order you would like them to appear (for example: Erica Heather Benstock ---> EBH)
